{"tid":1304415,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話警察仆街 教你反其道而行","createTime":"2019-07-10T15:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:24:06.000Z","uid":115660,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d20e17bd716ea036aced1bdb972111bd45a3efef","tid":1304415,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"呢招不適用大型示威現場 只適用小型場面如油塘戰役<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當有人大聲鬧 大打人 非禮 而警察唔拉<br />\n你應該向在場指揮作正式報案<br />\n同佢講你要報案 帶埋證人去 <br />\n有投訴者 有證人 佢都唔拉既話 <br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抄number 全程拍片<br />\n向警察投訴科投訴佢妨礙司法公正</span></span><br />\n帶埋證人去投訴<br />\n<br />\n記住份比投訴科既口供要非常詳盡<br />\n自己用電腦打出黎再交比佢地<br />\n時 地 人事發經過<br />\n有咁詳細得咁詳細<br />\n<br />\n如果投訴科唔告<br />\n搵監警會<br />\n<br />\n監警會唔告 搵議員<br />\n<br />\n重複以上步驟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點係以上所有步驟都係免費<br />\n一蚊都唔洗比<br />\n既然林鄭話行之有效<br />\n請大家善用香港仍然有既監管方法</span></span>"},{"pid":"8077fdb9d4e5ac098ae625ad7d694f76cef63956","tid":1304415,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:11:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ed3b5846b5af87c268bee1ff256db056631b475","tid":1304415,"uid":115660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你仲有權即時打999報警<br />\n要求報案中心比埋到場處理既警員number你方便作出投訴<br />\n<br />\n我地係市民 我地係佢地既服務對象<br />\n我地全部野跟情序做<br />\n記低曬<br />\n第日投訴就好易入</span></span>"},{"pid":"5daee410b72ac245802c67b8f0157c32984167c6","tid":1304415,"uid":21592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:15:55.000Z","msg":"黨國機器操控香港內幕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tvs7H4rmhw8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dtvs7H4rmhw8&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3a6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=3889d054\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tvs7H4rmhw8</a>"},{"pid":"aa8bbda9b